„Three Sheets to the wind“ by @cocktailsbyadam
•
1 oz @DenizenRum Merchant’s Reserve
½ oz @DenizenRum Vatted Dark
½ oz Fresh Lime Juice
½ oz Fresh Pineapple Juice
½ oz Passionfruit Purée
½ oz Coconut Cream
½ oz Demerara Syrup
2 dashes Aromatic Bitters
3 Fresh Blackberries
•
Recipe by @cocktailsbyadam
•

node.text:
SEA-GIN 💙🐚

By @erukos at @kuukrestaurant

„Sea Gin“
•
Tanqueray Ten Gin
St. Germain elderflower liquor
Rhodymenia pseudopalmata algae
Blue spirulina cyanobacteria -Blue algae- 
lemon juice
lemongrass and chamomile infusion

-> Sulfur hexafluoride as an atmosphere around the cocktail
-> Floating edible bubble with citrus aroma
•
